subject: Reappointment of a part-time member of the Social Security Tribunal
precis: Reappointment of Jean Lazure of Gatineau, Quebec, as a part-time member of the Social Security Tribunal, to hold office during good behaviour for a term of two years, effective February 1, 2026.
